This character is one of the backroom staff at the Moonstone Mask. She stays in her room unless the place is closed down.

She has separete selected for male of female players, as well as differing reactions for charisma of male players.

Her dialogue loops in on itself as she engages in small talk to the player. There is in incrementing local on that dialogue, and once it has reached a certain number, the player can initiate a fade to black sexual encounter. Then the frat boys arrive. How high the number is (the number of loops spent in small talk) depends on the charisma of the player. The local is hereafter identified as the "SmallTalk" local

If the SmallTalk local gets too low, she will set another local that marks her as unfriendly, and will switch to the starting condition appropriate for that.

You know, I was a little leery of writing this hooker at first. I though she might be a bit harsh, or too uncouth for the atmosphere we were trying to construct. But you know, it might just turn out that she has a heart of gold. Go figure.
